title: Ep. - 277 - TRISHELLE CANATELLA ON MARRIED AT FIRST SIGHT EXECUTIVE PRODUCER OF LOST RESORT
description:
Trishelle Canatella has appeared on MTV’s Real World: Las Vegas and The Challenge. She also happens to be a close friend of one of the grooms featured this season on Lifetime TV’s Married at First Sight. She gives an insider account on what happens when your friend marries a stranger on television.

 

Jessica Sebastian is the President of Sirens Media and Executive Producer of Lost Resort on TBS, which follows nine strangers at their breaking points to an exotic wellness retreat where they embark on a voyage of self-discovery against a tropical backdrop.
